# API Endpoints Overview

## Root
- `GET /` ‚Äì Health check (root endpoint)

## Applications (`/applications`)
- `POST /applications` ‚Äì Apply to a job (student)
- `GET /applications/my` ‚Äì Get current user's applications (student)
- `GET /applications/job/:jobId` ‚Äì Get applications for a specific job (company)

## Authentication (`/auth`)
- `POST /auth/register` ‚Äì Register a new user
- `POST /auth/login` ‚Äì Login
- `POST /auth/verify-email` ‚Äì Verify email with code
- `POST /auth/resend-code` ‚Äì Resend verification code
- `POST /auth/forgot-password` ‚Äì Initiate password reset
- `POST /auth/reset-password` ‚Äì Reset password with code

## Companies (`/companies`)
- `GET /companies` ‚Äì List all companies
- `GET /companies/:id` ‚Äì Get a company by ID
- `POST /companies` ‚Äì Create a company (company role, auth required)
- `PATCH /companies/:id` ‚Äì Update a company (company role, auth required)

## Images (`/images`)
- `POST /images/upload` ‚Äì Upload an image with metadata (auth required)
- `GET /images/entity/:type/:id` ‚Äì List images for a given entity type and ID
- `PUT /images/profile` ‚Äì Set/replace current user's profile image (auth required)
- `GET /images/profile/:userId` ‚Äì Get a user's profile image
- `DELETE /images/:imageId` ‚Äì Delete an image (auth required)

## Jobs (`/jobs`)
- `GET /jobs` ‚Äì List jobs with optional filters
- `GET /jobs/nearby?lat=...&lon=...&radius=...` ‚Äì Find nearby jobs
- `GET /jobs/:id` ‚Äì Get job details by ID
- `POST /jobs` ‚Äì Create a job (company role, auth required)
- `PATCH /jobs/:id` ‚Äì Update a job (company role, auth required)
- `DELETE /jobs/:id` ‚Äì Delete a job (company role, auth required)

## Testimonials (`/testimonials`)
- `GET /testimonials/featured` ‚Äì Get featured testimonials for homepage
- `GET /testimonials` ‚Äì List all testimonials
- `POST /testimonials` ‚Äì Create a new testimonial (auth required)

## Users (`/users`)
- *No routes defined in the current controller file.*
